---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="SubSentry — Privacy Policy">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-5 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">Last updated: March 6, 2026</p>

    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">SubSentry ("the App") is built by Justin Bundrick. This policy explains how your information is handled when you use SubSentry.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Data We Collect</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4"><strong class="text-white">Account information:</strong> When you sign in with Apple, Google, or email, we receive your name and email address solely to create your account. If you use Sign in with Apple's email relay, we only see the relay address.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4"><strong class="text-white">Subscription data:</strong> The subscriptions you add — names, amounts, dates, categories — are stored <strong class="text-white">locally on your device</strong> and optionally synced via Apple's iCloud (CloudKit) to your other devices.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4"><strong class="text-white">Email import (optional):</strong> If you use the AI email import feature, you paste or forward subscription-related emails into the app. The text is processed to extract subscription details. We do not store, read, or retain the email content after parsing.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Data We Do NOT Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 mb-4 space-y-1">
      <li>Bank credentials, credit card numbers, or financial account logins</li>
      <li>Browsing history or location data</li>
      <li>Usage analytics or advertising identifiers</li>
      <li>Contacts, photos, or other personal files</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Data Storage</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">All subscription data is stored locally on your device using Apple's secure storage. If you enable iCloud sync, data is stored in your personal iCloud account under Apple's privacy and encryption standards. We do not operate external servers that store your data.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Third-Party Services</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 mb-4 space-y-1">
      <li><strong class="text-white">Apple</strong> (Sign in with Apple, iCloud, StoreKit) — subject to <a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Apple's Privacy Policy</a></li>
      <li><strong class="text-white">Google</strong> (Google Sign-In) — subject to <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Google's Privacy Policy</a>. We only request basic profile info.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">In-App Purchases</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Purchases are processed entirely through Apple's App Store. We do not collect or have access to your payment information.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">SubSentry is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">You can delete all your data at any time by deleting the app and disabling iCloud sync. To request account deletion, contact us at the email below.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Changes</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">Questions? Email <a href="mailto:justinbundrick@gmail.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">justinbundrick@gmail.com</a></p>
  </div>
</Layout>
